  "title": "AI 读不懂文档结构？计算所重构 Agentic RAG 文档推理能力",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652683412&idx=3&sn=0e2c139705bb4725353a9759c106d3c0",
  "date": "2026-03-16 03:45:00",
